<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Hansen Helmsmids,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, und des Nykel Schersmids, ewrs
                                <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> czu rede gesaczt und der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> mitburger,
                        nihts schuldig sey. Deuht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ihts <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                        <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
